{
  "stem": "2804.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was a GI.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was a T/4.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he had a two weeks' leave.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in February, we went home, and we became engaged.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then when we went back to our respective camps during that time, I sent a letter to my mother, and he sent it to his mother.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they made the wedding.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They made the plans and got together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I went up in August, everything was set.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was married in Newark, New Jersey, August the 20th.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Part-- the family that was there came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It so happened that my husband had a younger brother who was stationed also in the-- he went into the army.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it seemed that his mother forgot to send him an invitation, and he didn't get a furlong or a leave, whatever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So his brother missed our wedding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But for our 50th anniversary, he was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[CHUCKLES]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I came back to Florida.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and he went back to his.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He went back to Texas.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And during that time, I thought, well, most of the general hospitals were stationed in the Midwest, the army hospitals.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went to my chief nurse, and I said that I would like to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] go into the-- I'll leave the Army Air Corps if I could and go into the-- and go into a general hospital, go into the army.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said, well, she would see what she could do about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I figured this way, maybe I would get nearer to Texas or any of the other general hospitals.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That way, we would maybe be able to see each other on a long weekend or whatever.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
